Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • lab.android.rwth.evgenijandkate.plugscontrolclient.model.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Created by ekaterina on 07.06.2015. A model class for the user entity. The user's logging name, password, ip address and the port value of the host he intends to reach, his first name and last name and whether he has administrative rights or not is being stored. In order to set all these values a builder pattern is used.
